    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Empowering Women in the Music Industry | Artist showcase - Day 3 |  Sat, May 2, 2026, 7:30 pm | Azrieli Studio"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40747/untitled_design_(3)__large.png"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "This event is part of the Empowering Women in the Music Industry Conference presented by Axé WorldFest in partnership with the National Arts Centre.\n\nShowcase schedule:\n\nDoors open – 7:00 PM\n\nAmanda Fox Jingle Dance Performance –  7:30 PM\n\nEmpress Nyiringango – 7:45 PM\n\nThe Pairs – 8:30 PM\n\nRachel Therrien – 9:30 PM\n\nAbout the conference:\n\nEWIMI6 is a three-day, multi-venue conference and showcase program featuring 17 events across 9 venues, including live and DJ showcases, networking, pitching, keynotes, panels, workshops, mentorship, and wellness activities. \n\nThe 2026 theme, Cultural Connectors, highlights artists and cultural workers as bridges..."
      }
    ],
